                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040111-43-off270 t18040111-43-cd271"></join>, three shillings and eighteen halfpence
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18040111-43-victim409" type="victimName">
                     Evan 
